node.text:
Welcome @rayssalealsk8 🧚‍♀️

She is the future of skateboarding. Everytime she skates she’s having so much fun and doing amazing things! I am so hyped to have her on @aprilskateboards and am looking forward to more good times and more skating in the future 🇧🇷🖤

node.text:
Back skating again 😍

I broke a couple ribs in Rome and have only been back on board for a few days. It’s a gooood feeling!
